{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778431170081,"sessionID":"ses_1ed3df8ffffekwLRU5gAIhDTy6","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_lHryA2zc5gt2deNsiLjsJpKB","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":2000},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"\\nNEW TERM\\nperoxisome-chloroplast membrane tether activity\\nThe binding activity of a molecule that brings together the peroxisome and the chloroplast membrane, establishing the localization of the peroxisome close to the chloroplast.\\nPMID:17215364\\n\\n* **GO term ID and Label**\\nGO:0010381  peroxisome-chloroplast membrane tethering\\nThe attachment of a peroxisome to a chloroplast via molecular tethers that physically bridge their respective membranes and attach them to each other. The tethering may facilitate exchange of metabolites between the organelles. PMID:17215364\\n\\n\\n* **Reason for deprecation** Put an x in the appropriate box: \\n\\n - [x] The reason for obsoletion is that this term represents a molecular function.\\n\\n\\n* **\\\"Consider\\\" term(s) (ID and label)**\\nSuggestions for reannotation\\n\\nNEW Term above, this is a MF\\n\\n* **Are there annotations to this term?**\\n- How many EXP: 1 (TAIR)\\n\\n* **Are there mappings and cross references to this term? (InterPro, Keywords; check QuickGO cross-references section)**\\n\\n* **Is this term in a subset? (check the AmiGO page for that term)**\\n\\n* **Any other information**\\n\\n\\n----\\nChecklist for ontology editor\\n\\n***Check term usage and metadata in Protégé***\\n- [ ] check term usage in the ontology \\n- [ ] check internal mappings: RHEA, EC, MetaCyc\\n- [ ] check subset usage\\n- [ ] check taxon constraints \\n\\n***Check annotations***\\n- [ ] create Annotation Review spreadsheet \\n- * Annotation Review template: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1izV3q1jnq_Ybg5MJ53O_b5BCTkGtjl_Fi-cOg3-7eBE/edit#gid=0\\n- * Instructions: https://wiki.geneontology.org/Annotation_Review_Request\\n- [ ] create annotation review ticket: https://github.com/geneontology/go-annotation/issues/new?assignees=&labels=annotation+review&template=annotation-review-for-obsoletion.md&title=Review+annotations+to+%5BINSERT+GO+TERM%5D\\n- [ ] find external mappings (via IEAS), include in obsoletion notice  \\n- [ ] tag curators in Annotation... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws7_ZBd9\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"New term added in PR #31929:\\n\\n**GO:7770065** peroxisome-chloroplast membrane tether activity (molecular_function)\\n\\nDefinition: \\\"The binding activity of a molecule that brings together the peroxisome membrane and the chloroplast membrane, establishing the localization of the peroxisome close to the chloroplast.\\\" [PMID:17215364]\\n\\nFollows the same pattern as other peroxisome-organelle membrane tether activity terms (GO:0160190 peroxisome-mitochondrion, GO:0160229 peroxisome-ER), placed under GO:0140177 membrane-membrane adaptor activity.\\n\\nThe obsoletion of GO:0010381 is not included in this PR and should be handled separately through the annotation review process.\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-20T22:48:11Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n16:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31877#issuecomment-4284749693\",\n17:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n18:     },\n19:     {\n20:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws7_ZRWL\",\n21:       \"author\": {\n22:         \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n23:       },\n24:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n25:       \"body\": \"[Term]\\nid: GO:7770065\\nname: peroxisome-chloroplast membrane tether activity\\nnamespace: molecular_function\\ndef: \\\"The binding activity of a molecule that brings together the peroxisome membrane and the chloroplast membrane, establishing the localization of the peroxisome close to the chloroplast.\\\" [PMID:17215364]\\nsynonym: \\\"peroxisome-chloroplast membrane adaptor activity\\\" EXACT []\\nis_a: GO:0140177 ! membrane-membrane adaptor activity\\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \\\"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31877\\\" xsd:anyURI\\ncreated_by: dragon-ai-agent\\ncreation_date: 2026-04-20T22:23:03Z\",\n26:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-20T23:02:42Z\",\n27:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n28:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n29:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n30:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n31:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31877#issuecomment-4284814731\",\n32:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n33:     },\n34:     {\n35:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAUBdnQ\",\n36:       \"author\": {\n37:         \"login\": \"tberardini\"\n38:       },\n39:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n40:       \"body\": \"@raymond91125 I don't see the new term in AmiGO or imported into our database yet. Is it in the public files? I will move the annotation when the new term is available for use.\",\n41:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-24T20:03:03Z\",\n42:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": true,\n43:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n44:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n45:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n46:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31877#issuecomment-4315962781\",\n47:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n48:     },\n49:     {\n50:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAUDVzw\",\n51:       \"author\": {\n52:         \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n53:       },\n54:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n55:       \"body\": \"@tberardini The new term GO:7770065 is in