 GO:0160229 peroxisome-ER), placed under GO:0140177 membrane-membrane adaptor activity.\\n\\nThe obsoletion of GO:0010381 is not included in this PR and should be handled separately through the annotation review process.\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-20T22:48:11Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31877#issuecomment-4284749693\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws7_ZRWL\",","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"__issue_context__.json","time":{"start":1778431170062,"end":1778431170076}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_02a1faa3f6ef04d6016a00b4c1d11081938733c336e823a545"}},"id":"prt_e12c2154d001lIwFmtCBaqeuUW","sessionID":"ses_1ed3df8ffffekwLRU5gAIhDTy6","messageID":"msg_e12c207b6001UqDIozy53BOz3R"}}
